description:
Feature Description : User navigates to alert console page, searches by Node Name, AlertMetric data and Alert Name
     verifies results should be based on the search input
name: Search Functionality with ITOps Admin role

steps.name: "Admin" enters project name as "Btest_RES_Aug30" in the search field
"admin" enters "node name" and clicks on enter "CNHKGG-00A-SSC1"
verify search result should contain all the alerts from the same node name "CNHKGG-00A-SSC1"
"admin" enters "alertMetric data" and clicks on enter "Node Down"
verify search result should contain all the alerts which has alert metric matching the search criteria "Node Down"
"admin" enters "alert name" and clicks on enter "Test case 29b"
verify search result should contain all the alerts which has alert name matching the search criteria "Test case 29b"
"admin" verifies BA label should be displayed along with base alert id in the 'Alert ID section' of child
"admin" verifies Severity strip should be shown for individual alert which is shown in search result, not cluster severity
"admin" verifies All console data should be for individual alerts data not cluster data
"admin" verifies Last alert time, "state/action" should be displayed
